Feature: cucumber feature
Scenario: Go to amazon page, login, search products and validate
Given Go to Amazon.com.mx
Given a - Login with valid credentials
And b - Search for product Samsung Galaxy S9 64GB 
And c - Select first product and save the price
And d - Click on the product
Then e -Validate first price vs detail price
When f - Click on Add to Cart
Then g - Validate again, first price vs current price
Then h - Validate that the Shop car has <1> as a number
When i - Search for another product: Alienware Aw3418DW
And j - Select First product
And k - Add to Cart
Then l - Verify that the cart number is now <2>
When m - End of test